caption: Path expression grammar
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/reference
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/reference/path-grammar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

```
path     := segment ( separator segment )*
segment  := key | "[" ( index | "*" ) "]"
key      := [^.[\]/]+                      (one or more non-reserved chars)
index    := [0-9]+
separator:= "." | (no separator before "[")
prefix   := ( ".." "/" )*                  (only in binding tokens)
```
